Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:43.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}就算誰都不曾見過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:47.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}美麗的東西就是美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:49.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我早已知曉
